Name: Car Crash Couch Party
About the game: Car Crash Couch Party is a local multiplayer party game meant to be played by a bunch of friends on a couch! You can play against your friends in the soccer mode, and shoot the soccer ball back and forth with your cannons! Or, you can compete in the Capture the Flag mode, and hit the enemy team with cannon balls to stop them from stealing your flag.
